///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

////////// Reminders Application created by Cameron Imanpour (CIMAN01@github.com) /////////////

///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

A console application that sets up a scheduled reminder for a task.

The user will schedule a specific task, with a time and date, how many times they wish

to repeat that specific task, and optionally enter any additional notes. All this will be

stored locally and the user can either confirm the schedule or start over. Once the schedule

is confirm, the data stored will be uploaded and send to the user's email account.


///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Flowchart:

1) - We ask user if they want set a reminder - yes/no?

a - if yes, we ask for all the necessary info
b - if no, we quit program

2) - once all necessary info entered, we ask for confirmation: yes/no?

a - if yes, upload reminder to servers (using api)
b - if no, we start over

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////